OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry
OL,6,Fevening with clear spells becoming
OL,7,Fmore prolonged as cloud clears.
OL,8,FRemaining dry overnight with long
OL,9,Fclear spells, leading to a cold night
OL,10,Fwith a frost.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA dry morning with some long
OL,13,Fspells of sunshine. Turning cloudier
OL,14,Fthrough the afternoon as rain spreads
OL,15,Feastwards.
